high_descs: Turn left, step forward to the bath tub, turn right and to the toilet.
Pick up the red rag on the left side.
Turn right, step forward, turn right and walk to the vanity.
Open the drawer under the vanity, place the rag inside, close the drawer.
Step forward to the vanity to get closer.
Pick up the red rag to the right of the sink.
Turn around, step forward, then turn around to face the vanity.
Open the vanity drawer and put the red rag inside, close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Pick up two rags and place in the vanity drawer.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the tub, then turn right and walk up to the toilet.
Pick up the red rag off of the tub.
Turn right and walk forward, then hang a right and walk over to the counter.
Open the upper right hand drawer of the counter and put the red rag inside, then close the drawer.
Walk up to the counter.
Pick up the red rag off of the counter.
Turn around and take a step forward, the turn around to face the counter.
Open the upper right hand drawer of the counter and put the red rag inside, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move two red rags into a drawer.

high_descs: Turn left, go forward, turn right, go forward
Pick up the cloth near the bath
Turn around, go to the counter
Put the cloth in the drawer
Turn up to the counter
Pick up the cloth on the counter
Turn around, go forward a bit, turn around
Put the cloth in the drawer
anns.task_desc: Put two clothes into the drawer
